701924f-a.title: Bronx: Unionport Road - Odell Street
701924f-a.text:
Unionport oad, n. fr. Cdell St., showing in the background, the new housing oevelooment of the Metropolitan Life Insurance Company, the Parkchester Houses.
Sept. 44, 1939
P. L. Sperr, photographer
701924f-a.folder: Unionport Road & Odell Street, Bronx, NY

701925f-c.title: Bronx: Unionport Road - Odell Street
701925f-c.text:
1400 and 1418 Unionport Road (left), east side, at its Junction with Odeil Street, showing two old fraame houses.
The view is northward.
July 9, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.
(s)
A view of the two houses ten years later, as seen from
O1mstead Avenue, at Benedict Avenue.
April 10, 193s.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
An exclusive view of No. 1400 Unionport Road.
April 10, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
